{"tid":1512563,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"依家支持港獨既人應該多過支持777","createTime":"2019-08-28T02:48:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T06:17:31.000Z","uid":218412,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e5d524285fbed7fab9ec1966a1435d451adc58ca","tid":1512563,"uid":218412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:48:29.000Z","msg":"上星期公佈既民意調查：<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究所8月中調查顯示，特首林鄭月娥最新的民望評分24.6分，較兩周前下跌3.3分，<span style=\"color: red;\">支持率17%</span>，反對率76%，支持度淨值為負59個百分點，全部數字較兩周前顯著轉差，研究所形容是「前無古人」，再創上任特首以來最差。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2437198\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2437198&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=a3820563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2437198</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2015年民意調查：<br />\n<br />\n中大的傳播與民意調查中心在七月訪問了超過一千名十五歲或以上的市民。調查首次問到香港人對二○四七年後香港前途問題的看法，<span style=\"color: red;\">當中有一成七受訪者支持香港獨立</span>，約有五成八受訪者反對港獨。約七成受訪者支持維持一國兩制，僅百分之六的受訪者反對維持一國兩制。約一成四受訪者支持香港全面由中國直接管治；反對的佔約五成九。調查結果亦顯示，愈年輕、教育程度愈高的受訪者，愈傾向支持港獨。<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/1317225/日報\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F1317225%2F%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=516cce10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F1317225%2F%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1&h=47cadd45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/1317225/日報</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然港獨支持率係17年6月又跌番去11%：<br />\n<br />\n中大傳播與民意調查中心近日公布一項有逾千人參與的民調結果，其中市民對2047年後香港的看法出現變化，<span style=\"color: red;\">支持「香港獨立」的支持度比去年同一調查減少6個百分點，由17.4%下跌至11.4%</span>，至於「維持一國兩制」及「全面由中國直接管治」的支持度就出現微升。另外，逾六成受訪者認為本港社會狀況比20年前差，19.2%認為「差不多」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/96949/中大民調-港獨支持度17-4-跌至11-4-六成稱回歸20年社會變差\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F96949%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF-%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%BA%A617-4-%E8%B7%8C%E8%87%B311-4-%E5%85%AD%E6%88%90%E7%A8%B1%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B820%E5%B9%B4%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E8%AE%8A%E5%B7%AE&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=bdfb5e63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/96949/中大民調-港獨支持度17-4-跌至11-4-六成稱回歸20年社會變差</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係經過呢兩個月，我相信港獨派人數已經超越魚蛋果時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望可以再做多次港獨民調為我地打下氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72abe17d45a4cbd7f0013a44e326f800aef23198","tid":1512563,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=3240ea8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=5b40bf26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=ac4052e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"35bba31dcf100372a6b5fcdcf79f1c562a4df9a3","tid":1512563,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:48:57.000Z","msg":"出POST打錯日期 應該係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8月28同8月29號</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港自由之書&mdash;&mdash;報應來了，街站收集投訴信</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1510955/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1510955/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2deb715db468f9252a040123dd5b8814bfe0389a","tid":1512563,"uid":89145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:49:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5509e9db11c570ca2e8968e6049d48f6f824f28d","tid":1512563,"uid":218412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:50:50.000Z","msg":"留左位比呂麗乳搖後推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45182f32b3113ed917951a60e1c30a3c1c435506","tid":1512563,"uid":218412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:51:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03d6f0bbd178511e5cd4c0a57e037d7d67916bde","tid":1512563,"uid":218412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:51:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a583608ab5d917b308267191a15e193c2d4087c0","ti